{"tid":2510030,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"不讓SpaceX專美在前 藍色起源宣布開賣太空船位","createTime":"2021-04-30T01:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T07:36:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3b4883b56a895c51fcbb375caa96b325af5ff884","tid":2510030,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕亞馬遜執行長貝佐斯與特斯拉執行長馬斯克除了在世界首富的地位競爭外，兩人的太空公司藍色起源與SpaceX間的比拚也相當激烈。在SpaceX日前徵求素人上太空後，藍色起源也宣布將開賣首批太空船船位。<br />\n<br />\n藍色起源發布一段50秒短片，由貝佐斯親自上陣，揭露其火箭「新雪帕德」近年來的測試情況，影片最後強調「是時候了」，要大家到網站上註冊以便獲得更多新雪帕德首批座位資訊，細節則會在當地時間5月5日公布。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3516340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3516340&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f86958ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3516340&h=7fa6fa37\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3516340</a>"},{"pid":"cc283f8c8a6dc6c65b119746e6771f9ab2923001","tid":2510030,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:01:19.000Z","msg":"can't get it up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267ca21fddf66af781a402e7bbbe2fae00bc6197","tid":2510030,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:10:50.000Z","msg":"get it up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfd21e256993b8aa0f2991ef4db6a077a0ed81b","tid":2510030,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:27:44.000Z","msg":"炒概念"},{"pid":"9131444564c811ac8f0ea3c6a31a7d0b14cea3b7","tid":2510030,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:34:08.000Z","msg":"兩個有錢佬狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181de0aab36a6